aku diminta duduk di depan kanvas

1122
01:22:10,717 --> 01:22:13,512
dan disuruh melukis.

1123
01:22:14,638 --> 01:22:19,643
Katanya, "Pejamkan matamu
dan katakan warna apa yang kau rasakan."

1124
01:22:20,477 --> 01:22:21,687
Jadi, kujawab,

1125
01:22:23,355 --> 01:22:24,355
"Biru."

1126
01:22:25,357 --> 01:22:28,152
Dia membimbingku melukis ombak.

1127
01:22:29,570 --> 01:22:30,946
Lalu dia bertanya,

1128
01:22:32,698 --> 01:22:33,824
"Apa kau marah?"

1129
01:22:34,324 --> 01:22:36,452
Kujawab, "Ya."

1130
01:22:37,035 --> 01:22:38,370
Lalu dia berkata,

1131
01:22:38,454 --> 01:22:41,248
"Bagiku, itu warna merah."

1132
01:22:41,331 --> 01:22:43,000
Jadi, akhirnya aku duduk

1133
01:22:44,334 --> 01:22:47,171
di depan kanvas dengan ombak biru…

1134
01:22:49,631 --> 01:22:51,133
dan garis merah.

1135
01:22:51,675 --> 01:22:54,636
Hasilnya berantakan.
Kau tahu apa yang dia lakukan?

1136
01:22:55,637 --> 01:22:56,638
Tidak.

1137
01:23:03,437 --> 01:23:04,646
Dia merampungkannya.

1138
01:23:07,816 --> 01:23:12,321
Lalu dipajang di kanopi atas ranjang.

1139
01:23:13,655 --> 01:23:15,073
Suatu pagi,

1140
01:23:15,157 --> 01:23:18,076
aku mendongak dan melihat lukisan wajahku.

1141
01:23:19,036 --> 01:23:20,454
Menakjubkan.

1142
01:23:22,915 --> 01:23:24,458
Aku hanya kanvas

1143
01:23:25,375 --> 01:23:27,711
yang dia mainkan sampai selesai.

1144
01:23:28,754 --> 01:23:30,881
Tapi dia punya banyak kanvas.

1145
01:23:32,466 --> 01:23:35,511
Ada berlapis-lapis.

1146
01:23:40,307 --> 01:23:41,683
Lihat ekspresimu.

1147
01:24:30,566 --> 01:24:32,234
- Hei.
- Hei.

1148
01:24:34,069 --> 01:24:35,279
Kau sulit dihubungi.

1149
01:24:36,238 --> 01:24:37,238
Ya, aku sibuk.

1150
01:24:41,743 --> 01:24:42,743
Kau tahu…

1151
01:24:44,580 --> 01:24:46,081
aku optimistis.

1152
01:24:46,873 --> 01:24:48,000
Ini gara-gara kau.

1153
01:25:11,231 --> 01:25:13,734
Sudah lama aku tak sedamai ini.

1154
01:25:22,242 --> 01:25:23,452
Sayang, kau tak apa?

1155
01:25:27,706 --> 01:25:28,706
Mea?

1156
01:25:34,254 --> 01:25:35,254
Mea, tunggu!

1157
01:25:45,349 --> 01:25:47,100
MATI KAU, JALANG
KAU HANCURKAN HIDUPKU

1158
01:25:47,184 --> 01:25:48,310
Tunggu. Kau salah paham.

1159
01:25:48,977 --> 01:25:52,439
Mea, aku mohon.
Biar kujelaskan. Kau salah paham.

1160
01:25:52,522 --> 01:25:54,524
Cari pengacara lain. Aku berhenti!

1161
01:25:54,608 --> 01:25:56,693
Aku menulis itu gara-gara videonya.

1162
01:25:57,569 --> 01:25:58,569
Sudah cukup.

1163
01:26:00,113 --> 01:26:02,199
Kumohon. Sudah terlambat untuk mundur.

1164
01:26:02,282 --> 01:26:04,076
Aku butuh kau, Mea. Ya, Tuhan…

1165
01:26:07,746 --> 01:26:09,623
Kau copot lukisan wajahku,

1166
01:26:09,706 --> 01:26:13,085
